WEBVTT

1
00:20:38.360 --> 00:20:39.860 
对不起
I'm sorry.

2
00:20:47.200 --> 00:20:49.160 
你怎么这么讨厌他
Why are you so against him?

3
00:20:49.240 --> 00:20:52.040 
除了因为他要抢我们的遗产吗
Aside from the fact he's planning to steal our inheritance?

4
00:20:52.160 --> 00:20:53.910 
是你的遗产
Your inheritance.

5
00:20:54.330 --> 00:20:56.790 
跟茜玻和我没有关系
It makes no difference to Sybil and me.

6
00:20:56.880 --> 00:20:59.630 
反正遗产没我们的份
We won't inherit, whatever happens.

7
00:20:59.920 --> 00:21:01.630 
他不上档次
He isn't one of us.

8
00:21:01.710 --> 00:21:03.810 
弗雷迪堂哥也学法律
Cousin Freddie's studying for the bar,

9
00:21:03.810 --> 00:21:05.300 
维安·麦克唐纳也是
and so is Vivian MacDonald.

10
00:21:05.380 --> 00:21:06.870 
他们上的可是林肯律师院
At Lincoln's Inn.

11
00:21:05.380 --> 00:21:06.870 
英国四大律师学院之首

12
00:21:06.870 --> 00:21:09.040 
亲爱的玛丽

13
00:21:06.870 --> 00:21:09.640 
不是在什么里彭的破烂事务所工作
Not sitting at a dirty little desk in Ripon.

